{
  "texts": [
    "Here we present ClimSight, a simple prototype demonstration tool for such a novel climate information system.",
    "We argue that with a moderate amount of development and access to more advanced climate model output-including global km-scale simulations-large-language-modelbased systems can provide actionable climate information to anyone with access to a computer.",
    "We built ClimSight to combine the strength of large language models with geographical information about the location of interest and climate information from model simulations.",
    "Consider an individual who owns a parcel of land in Morocco and contemplates its use for wheat cultivation.",
    "They are aware of changes in the climate, and concerned regarding potential impacts on their agricultural venture."
  ]
}